<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #2c5aa0;
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .invoice-details {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 15px;
        border-left: 4px solid #2c5aa0;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 15px;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
        border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
      }
      .amount {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #2c5aa0;
      }
      .contact-info {
        margin-top: 15px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #666;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>🧾 Invoice from Atma Nirbhar Farm</h1>
      <p>Your monthly delivery invoice is ready!</p>
    </div>

    <p>Dear <%= @customer.name %>,</p>

    <p>We hope this email finds you well! Please find your invoice for <%= @invoice.invoice_date.strftime('%B %Y') %> attached to this email.</p>

    <div class="invoice-details">
      <h3>Invoice Details:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Invoice Number:</strong> <%= @invoice.formatted_number %></li>
        <li><strong>Invoice Date:</strong> <%= @invoice.invoice_date.strftime('%d %B %Y') %></li>
        <li><strong>Due Date:</strong> <%= @invoice.due_date.strftime('%d %B %Y') %></li>
        <li class="amount"><strong>Total Amount:</strong> ₹<%= number_with_delimiter(@invoice.total_amount) %></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h3>📦 Order Summary:</h3>
    <% @invoice_items.each do |item| %>
      <p>• <%= item.product.name %> - Quantity: <%= item.quantity %> <%= item.product.unit_type %> @ ₹<%= item.unit_price %> = ₹<%= number_with_delimiter(item.quantity * item.unit_price) %></p>
    <% end %>

    <% if @delivery_assignments.any? %>
      <p><strong>📅 Total Deliveries:</strong> <%= @delivery_assignments.count %> deliveries completed this month</p>
    <% end %>

    <% if @has_pdf_attachment %>
      <div style="background-color: #d4edda; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #28a745;">
        <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #155724;">📎 PDF Invoice Attached</h4>
        <p style="margin: 0; color: #155724;">The detailed PDF invoice is attached to this email for your records and printing. This PDF can be opened on any device and includes all delivery details.</p>
      </div>
    <% elsif @has_html_attachment %>
      <div style="background-color: #e3f2fd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;">
        <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #1976d2;">📄 HTML Invoice Attached</h4>
        <p style="margin: 0; color: #1976d2;">Your invoice is attached as an HTML file (can be opened in any browser). For the best experience, use the online link below.</p>
      </div>
    <% else %>
      <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;">
        <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #856404;">⚠️ Attachment Not Available</h4>
        <p style="margin: 0; color: #856404;">Attachment could not be generated. Please use the online link below to view your invoice.</p>
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <div style="background-color: #e3f2fd; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center; border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;">
      <h4 style="margin: 0 0 15px 0; color: #1976d2;">🌐 View Invoice Online</h4>
      <p style="margin: 0 0 15px 0; color: #1976d2;">You can also view and download your invoice online anytime:</p>
      <a href="<%= @public_url %>"
         style="display: inline-block; background-color: #2196f3; color: white; padding: 12px 25px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;">
        📄 View Invoice Online
      </a>
      <p style="margin: 15px 0 0 0; font-size: 12px; color: #666;">
        💡 This link works on any device and doesn't expire. Bookmark it for future reference!
      </p>
    </div>

    <p><strong>💳 Payment Instructions:</strong><br>
    Please make your payment by the due date mentioned above. You can scan the UPI QR code in the invoice or contact us for other payment methods.</p>

    <p>Thank you for choosing Atma Nirbhar Farm for your fresh milk delivery needs. We appreciate your continued trust in our services!</p>

    <div class="footer">
      <h4>🏠 Atma Nirbhar Farm</h4>
      <div class="contact-info">
        📍 Bangalore<br>
        📞 +91 9972808044 | +91 9008860329<br>
        📱 WhatsApp: +91 9972808044<br>
        📧 atmanirbharfarmbangalore@gmail.com
      </div>
      <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-style: italic; color: #888;">
        Fresh milk delivered with care, every day! 🥛
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>